    "causal_summary": "The `system-skill-advisor` skill ships a 46-scenario manual testing playbook (`manual_testing_playbook/`) spanning native MCP tools, CLI runtime hooks, compatibility shims, auto-update daemon state, auto-indexing, lifecycle routing, scorer fusion and Python compatibility. The playbook had not been executed end-to-end against the current build, so its real PASS/PARTIAL/FAIL/SKIP state and any drift between documented expected signals and live behavior were unknown.",
